
Codebook

Data Information

Original data: https://d396qusza40orc.cloudfront.net/getdata%2Fprojectfiles%2FUCI%20HAR%20Dataset.zip
Original description of the dataset: http://archive.ics.uci.edu/ml/datasets/Human+Activity+Recognition+Using+Smartphones

Script Detail

Merges the training and the test sets to create one data set.
Extracts only the measurements on the mean and standard deviation for each measurement.
Uses descriptive activity names to name the activities in the data set.
Appropriately labels the data set with descriptive activity names.
Creates a second, independent tidy data set with the average of each variable for each activity and each subject.

Script Function

Load librairies dplyr and stringr.
Load all data and create objects.
Rename Columns for test and train (separately) to make data tidy.
Rename Activity Labels for test and train.
Create object that combines all test and all train data.
Merge both datasets
Create new dataset of the mean of each variable for each activity and each subject

